{
  "stem": "512.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they took away the license from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Like my father was a butcher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He wasn't allowed to kill-- slaughtering, excuse me, slaughtering the animals.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Or having the butcher store, this was forbidden for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So they would bribe, sometimes, officials that would let him in the non-kosher slaughter house have the schochet, which was called, come in and slaughter, that the Jews should have a little meat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But this was-- so they-- those that they were working hand in hand, they would give them the non-kosher part of the meat because, you know, there is an animal that is kosher part and non-kosher part.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they let them have it for nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But then they went and they turned on them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they called up the authorities and say go confiscate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they would arrest them and they would torture them to say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it was hell through the years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very-- while Czechoslovakia-- while we were under Czechoslovakia, it was liberal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they were holding it, but they-- it wasn't and open anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when they had the authority, they took advantage fully.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the community, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would-- any little thing that they saw that they knew that wasn't right, they reported the Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those that had license on selling various things, they would say, on the QT, he is selling it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would-- they would always find reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like for instance, even later one we were given rations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they would report, she sold her rations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother was mostly alone because my father was again in the service from 1941 or '42, taken in the Hungarian service as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not in a uniform, but with civilian clothes, with the yellow bands, with the stars.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
